**Target:** Proposal for a regulation — Article 3 — paragraph 1 — point 16

## Text proposed by the Commission

(16) ‘recall of an AI system’ means any measure aimed at achieving the return to the provider of an AI system made available to users ;

(16)

(16)

## Amendment of the European Parliament

(16) ‘recall of an AI system’ means any measure aimed at achieving the return to the provider of an AI system that has been made available to deployers ;

‘recall of an AI system’ means any measure aimed at achieving the return to the provider of an AI system made available to users ;

‘recall of an AI system’ means any measure aimed at achieving the return to the provider of an AI system that has been made available to deployers ;

